        "title": "running a batch file through java program",
        "body": "<p>I want to run a batch file through java program. The batch file itself runs a exe file with some filename as arguments. I tried this by creating a C program and running that exe through java. Is there any other way to run a batch file which itself runs a exe through java. Thanks in advance...   <\/p>\n",
